/* 
===BLOCK===

-will take full width,If you do not specify the offer.
-Put a break between it and the other element.
-respect padding,margin,width,height.
*/


/* 
===INLINE===

-don't respect width and height.
-didn't Put a break between it and the other element.
-respect padding and margin but just [left,right].
-allow elements before and after it.

*/


/* 
===INLINE-BLOCK===

-allow elements before and after it.
-respect padding,margin,width,height.
*/


/* 
===NONE===

-Hide an element without reserving its place.
*/


/* 
===visibility: hidden===

-To hide an element while reserving its place.
*/


/* THE USEFULL KEY FOR BLOCK,INLINE,INLINE-BLOCK=display */
